The '''Class-C thermal detonator''' was a type of [[Thermal detonator/Legends|thermal detonator]] used by [[Aurra Sing/Legends|Aurra Sing]] in [[40 ABY/Legends|40 ABY]]. They were also used by [[YVH 1]] [[Droid/Legends|droids]] on the [[Mission to Myrkr|Myrkr mission]] to supposedly clear out three [[voxyn]] in the interior of the ''[[Exquisite Death]]''.

